{"title":"Mysql命令","slug":"Mysql命令","date":"2019-11-10T09:46:57.000Z","updated":"2019-11-24T05:20:48.329Z","comments":true,"excerpt":"<p>数据库Mysql的操作指令</p>","content":"<p>数据库Mysql的操作指令</p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n\n<h1 id=\"MySQL小结\"><a href=\"#MySQL小结\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"MySQL小结\"></a>MySQL小结</h1><h3 id=\"1-数据库的操作\"><a href=\"#1-数据库的操作\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1.数据库的操作\"></a>1.数据库的操作</h3><p>(1)创建数据库</p>\n<p>CREATE DATABASE 数据库名;</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">mysql&gt; CREATE DATABASE stu;</span><br><span class=\"line\">Query OK, 1 row affected</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>(2)进入数据库</p>\n<p>USE 数据库名;</p>\n<p>只有先进入数据库，才能进行下面的操作</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">mysql&gt; USE stu;</span><br><span class=\"line\">Database changed</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>(3)删除数据库</p>\n<p>DROP DATABASE 数据库名;</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">mysql&gt; DROP DATABASE stu;</span><br><span class=\"line\">Query OK, 0 rows affected</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>(4)创建数据表</p>\n<p>CREATE TABLE 表名(字段1 类型,字段2 类型……..);</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">mysql&gt; CREATE TABLE student(id int(10),name varchar(20));</span><br><span class=\"line\">Query OK, 0 rows affected</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>(5)查询表的结构信息</p>\n<p>DESC 表名;</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">mysql&gt; DESC student;</span><br><span class=\"line\">+-------+-------------+------+-----+---------+-------+</span><br><span class=\"line\">| Field | Type        | Null | Key | Default | Extra |</span><br><span class=\"line\">+-------+-------------+------+-----+---------+-------+</span><br><span class=\"line\">| id    | int(10)     | YES  |     | NULL    |       |</span><br><span class=\"line\">| name  | varchar(20) | YES  |     | NULL    |       |</span><br><span class=\"line\">+-------+-------------+------+-----+---------+-------+</span><br><span class=\"line\">2 rows in set</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>(6)查询表的创建信息</p>\n<p>SHOW CREATE TABLE 表名;</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">mysql&gt; SHOW CREATE TABLE student;</span><br><span class=\"line\">+---------+---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+</span><br><span class=\"line\">| Table   | Create Table                                                                                                              |</span><br><span class=\"line\">+---------+---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+</span><br><span class=\"line\">| student | CREATE TABLE `student` (</span><br><span class=\"line\">  `id` int(10) DEFAULT NULL,</span><br><span class=\"line\">  `name` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL</span><br><span class=\"line\">) ENGINE=MyISAM DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 |</span><br><span class=\"line\">+---------+---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+</span><br><span class=\"line\">1 row in set</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>(7)删除表</p>\n<p>DROP TABLE 表名;</p>\n<h3 id=\"2-修改表结构\"><a href=\"#2-修改表结构\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.修改表结构\"></a>2.修改表结构</h3><p>(1)修改表名</p>\n<p>ALTER TABLE 旧表名 RENAME 新表名;</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">mysql&gt; ALTER TABLE student RENAME studentinfo;</span><br><span class=\"line\">Query OK, 0 rows affected</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>(2)修改数据类型</p>\n<p>ALTER TABLE 表名 MODIFY 字段名 新类型;</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">mysql&gt; ALTER TABLE studentinfo MODIFY id varchar(25);</span><br><span class=\"line\">Query OK, 0 rows affected</span><br><span class=\"line\">Records: 0  Duplicates: 0  Warnings: 0</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>(3)修改字段名</p>\n<p>ALTER TABLE 表名 CHANGE 旧字段名 新字段名 新数据类型;</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">mysql&gt; ALTER TABLE studentinfo CHANGE id stuID varchar(25);</span><br><span class=\"line\">Query OK, 0 rows affected</span><br><span class=\"line\">Records: 0  Duplicates: 0  Warnings: 0</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>(4)删除字段</p>\n<p>ALTER TABLE 表名 DROP 字段名;</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">mysql&gt; ALTER TABLE studentinfo DROP stuID;</span><br><span class=\"line\">Query OK, 0 rows affected</span><br><span class=\"line\">Records: 0  Duplicates: 0  Warnings: 0</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>(5)添加字段</p>\n<p>ALTER TABLE 表名 ADD 新字段名 新字段类型;</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">mysql&gt; ALTER TABLE studentinfo ADD id varchar(40);</span><br><span class=\"line\">Query OK, 0 rows affected</span><br><span class=\"line\">Records: 0  Duplicates: 0  Warnings: 0</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"3-数据约束\"><a href=\"#3-数据约束\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3.数据约束\"></a>3.数据约束</h3><p>(1)数据约束</p>\n<p>主键，外键，非空，默认，唯一</p>\n<p>(2)主键</p>\n<p>PRIMARY KEY 写在字段类型后面</p>\n<p>主键特征：非空且唯一</p>\n<p>(3)主键自增</p>\n<p>AUTO_INCREMENT 写在字段类型后面主键之前</p>\n<p>(4)外键</p>\n<p>从表的外键，必须在主表的主键中出现，写在创建语句的最后面</p>\n<p>FOREIGN KEY (字段名) REFERENCES 主表名 (字段名)；</p>\n<p>(5)非空约束</p>\n<p>NOT NULL 写在字段类型后面</p>\n<p>(6)默认</p>\n<p>DEFAULT 默认值，如果默认值是字符的需要将字符加单引号</p>\n<p>(7)唯一</p>\n<p>UNIQUE 写在字段类型后面</p>\n","thumbnail":"/img/timg.jpg","primarycolor":"blueGrey","accentcolor":"blueGrey","categories":[],"tags":[]}